metadata.name: FreeRoss #1
metadata.description: FREE ROSS is a collection of 100 NFTs created by talented digital artists and staunch supporters of the crypto community. We have recreated these beautiful artworks based on the story and artworks of Ross Ulbricht. We will donate half of the proceeds to Ross/FreeRossDAO when each piece in the collection is sold. The buyers of 2 or more NFTs will receive a special edition as a recognition and appreciation token for their contributions. Follow @FreeRossNFT to claim your reward.
